normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fa03c21c500e393dcf23e33cf30b480f5055ce","tid":569751,"uid":38554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d938d160c0b8b5c9a347192305f6603366f3a161","tid":569751,"uid":79023,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美籍華裔咪即係中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>美國籍, 眼盲<br />\n係中國人仲俾佢入軍校?<br />\n不過早知有五毛咁講</blockquote><br />\n黃皮膚黑眼睛就係中國人架啦，加個美籍頭銜咪又係流緊中國人既血"},{"pid":"162b0496309c0504340c28f0bf9a554fa6f06850","tid":569751,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"文明地方出世係唔同d"},{"pid":"bef99715a4b23c5a3c5f5c0f8fa904ae410e33cc","tid":569751,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1df0f2bd6bde6d511f075edbf256d16b1ab591e7","tid":569751,"uid":48083,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"d66da336a5f17e25f6ee075baf50d8b262582aa7","tid":569751,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":49,"score":-48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"美國籍, 眼盲<br />\n係中國人仲俾佢入軍校?<br />\n不過早知有五毛咁講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"五毛係咁上下質素啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a60ecf80a6e683ac6f8b91488f14cba63e3a2f","tid":569751,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3fbb8e64ab40628f945496b7cb210fdf05c811a","tid":569751,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:29:55.000Z","msg":"美藉華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3098d754fc32bc1f1d219fb7d61ec65f8a54d4c","tid":569751,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"原來真係有人叫peter"},{"pid":"6f020997285d0900c8539f08c1fbad5a58b3a20b","tid":569751,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d938d160c0b8b5c9a347192305f6603366f3a161","tid":569751,"uid":79023,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美籍華裔咪即係中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>美國籍, 眼盲<br />\n係中國人仲俾佢入軍校?<br />\n不過早知有五毛咁講</blockquote><br />\n黃皮膚黑眼睛就係中國人架啦，加個美籍頭銜咪又係流緊中國人既血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"好多上將都係西點出黎 但西點無錢又係可以行埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68213a3fcb5096fa64f037d249f913fedda97151","tid":569751,"uid":72058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f1f9c8c27c53740b984206f2598148dad8bcb7","tid":569751,"uid":19920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"捨已為人 無論佢咩身分都值得敬佩"},{"pid":"606b3d5f579cff318b891e37c0591557a92a5760","tid":569751,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 儘管他擁美國國籍 首先他是個中國人"},{"pid":"4cfa6ccc167c179f8f13c2554f8ba0299d5c32cb","tid":569751,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"校警有槍都唔敢入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015af805de6645d9e2d4603e2bc45969ac2731f5","tid":569751,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n《Heavy》報導，王孟傑是移民二代，出生於紐約布魯克林區，而後隨著父母搬到美國佛羅里達州成長，他底下還有兩個年幼弟弟，爸媽經營一家中式餐館。<br />\n<br />\n他父親當年是偷渡來美，而後與母親相戀結婚。<br />\n<br />\n剛在美國上學的時候，王孟傑也曾經因為膚色的關係而受到同學的欺侮和歧視，不過他很勇敢，對每個人都十分真誠友善，也正是如此熱心助人的態度，讓他漸漸受人敬重。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n畀鬼仔欺凌都仲係真心愛國<br />\n難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}